<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Book outgoing items</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select by choosing <strong>YES</strong> or <strong>NO</strong> whether outgoing items should be booked when the order confirmation is generated.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Change order status to status</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Choose an order status to which the order is to be changed after the order confirmation is generated. If you don’t want the order status to change, select <strong>No change</strong> .</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Comment</strong></p></td>
